            <xar:mlstring>What is it?</xar:mlstring>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align:left;">
            <xar:mlstring>"The MyBookmarks module gives your users a way to add their favorite bookmarks to a sitewide database. The Bookmarks block with each users own bookmarks, will be displayed on thier Roles MyAccount page. The Random Bookmarks block will pull a random link from the master database of all users bookmarks."</xar:mlstring>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="xar-mod-title" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; width: auto; border-width: 1px; border-color: #B3B3B3; border-style: none none dotted none;">
            <xar:mlstring>How to use it?</xar:mlstring>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align:left;">
            <xar:mlstring>"You will need to create a new Privilege Called Addmybookmarks with Add rights and assign it to the Users Group, this will allow each user to add bookmarks."</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>"From the Admin menu you will see a listing of all bookmarks added by all users, so you have access to modify, or delete bookmarks."</xar:mlstring>
            <br />

        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="xar-mod-title" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; width: auto; border-width: 1px; border-color: #B3B3B3; border-style: none none dotted none;">
