            <xar:mlstring>"Random Bookmarks"</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>"Bookmarks"</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>"Top Bookmarks"</xar:mlstring>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align:left;">
            <xar:mlstring>The Booksmarks Module has three blocks included at this time.</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>Random Bookmarks -> Display's a random bookmark from the entire collection of Bookmarks'</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>Bookmarks -> Display's users bookmarks, when on the Roles Your Account page.'</xar:mlstring>
            <xar:mlstring>Top Bookmarks -> Display's the top rated bookmarks'.</xar:mlstring>
            
